<br>
Reserve Fri-Sat-Sun.<br>
<br>
Friday guild zones in, beats their way up and whacks the pegasi (Necros pray for their drop).  Camp for the night.<br>
<br>
Sat log in whack the pegasi again (Necros pray some more).  Work your way up as far as you can go.  Triad made it all the way up on day two and farmed for a mage crown.<br>
<br>
